<BaseLayout title="How to Describe Clothing and Materials" description="Prompt clothing, materials, layers, and accessories clearly." canonicalPath="/guides/clothing-prompts/"><article class="content-section article-body"><h1>How to Describe Clothing and Materials</h1><p>Useful clothing prompts mention garment type, material, color, fit, and accessories. “Layered linen tunic, apron pockets, small satchel, simple cloak” is more actionable than “nice fantasy outfit.”</p><p>Keep designs original. Do not rely on brand names, celebrity styling, or protected character costumes.</p></article></BaseLayout>
